 <br/>
I anledning af åbningen af Earth | Tree vil vi gerne give jer et gratis CC-medlemskab.<br/>
 <br/>
Installationen, Earth | Tree, er skabt af den verdensberømte arkitekt Kengo Kuma/KKAA og bygget af det mest grundlæggende, I kender: tegl og træ – valgt for deres taktile kvaliteter, deres historie og deres forankring i både japansk og nordisk natursyn.<br/>
 <br/>
Det gratis medlemskab er vores hyldest til jer, hvis faglighed og materialeforståelse installationen hviler på.<br/>
 <br/>
Medlemskabet giver adgang til udstillingen + alle øvrige medlemsfordele i hele perioden.<br/>
 <br/>
Kender du en i branchen, der burde se dette? Så del endelig budskabet.<br/>
 <br/>
Læs mere og bliv CC-håndværker-medlem via link i bio.<br/>
<br/>
🪚🧱 Calling all carpenters, bricklayers, joiners and cabinetmakers in Denmark – and students in these trades!<br/>
 <br/>
To mark the opening of Earth | Tree, we would like to offer you a free CC membership.<br/>
 <br/>
The installation, Earth | Tree, is created by world-renowned architect Kengo Kuma/KKAA and built from the most fundamental materials you know: brick and wood – chosen for their tactile qualities, their history and their roots in both Japanese and Nordic relationships with nature.<br/>
 <br/>
The free membership is our tribute to you, whose craft and understanding of materials the installation is built upon.<br/>
 <br/>
The membership gives access to the exhibition + all other membership benefits throughout the entire period.<br/>
 <br/>
Do you know someone in the industry who should see this? Please share the message.<br/>
 <br/>
Read more and become a CC craft member via the link in bio.</p><p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/DWT-VFJjVoH/">Se slideshow på Instagram</a></p>]]></description>
